---
title: Kickin' Crispy Honey Chicken with Mashed Sweet Potatoes and Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Coat chicken in breadcrumbs and immediately become a mealtime MVP. Crispy chicken is pretty much perfect in any form, but this isn’t your run-of-the-mill schnitzel. This version amps up the flavor, with blackening spices added to both the chicken itself and the panko breadcrumbs. After crisping up in the pan, the cutlets receive a drizzle of honey and a sprinkle of chili for a sweet-and-spicy-sensation.  We’re serving these alongside a heap of creamy mashed sweet potatoes and simply roasted Brussels sprouts, because you deserve maximum deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w8-r14-crispy-honey-chicken-cutlets-fe494de0.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w8-r14-crispy-honey-chicken-cutlets-5c3cad8cc445fa1f8055a332-7850634f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/2019-w8-r14-crispy-honey-chicken-cutlets-5c3cad8cc445fa1f8055a332
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 610 kcal
